snippet.title: DanceDanceRevolution EXTRA MIX (PlayStation / 2001) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
I took a break from beatmania to return to my original love: DDR.  Decided to record some gameplay of what I consider to be an underrated "mix" (really a compilation of songs from DDR Solo BASS MIX, Solo 2000 and 4th Mix Plus).  Nowhere else will you hear the likes of "My Baby Mama" and frankly, I think that's a crime.  So here's DanceDanceRevolution EXTRA MIX, emulated via Mednafen 0.9.41.

1:32 ANQUETTE - MY BABY MAMA
3:31 NAOKI 190 - HYSTERIA
5:32 POPULA DEMAND feat. THE GET FRESH GIRLS - DON'T CLOCK ME
7:26 Cydney D - Club Tropicana
9:24 200 - PARANOIA EVOLUTION
11:40 N.M.R - CELEBRATE NITE
13:37 BAMBEE - Typical Tropical
15:31 FACTOR-X - WILD RUSH
17:36 CAPTAIN JACK - DRILL INSTRUCTOR (C-Jah Happy Mix)
19:30 NW260 - DROP OUT
21:25 Credits / BeForU - DIVE

If there are any specific songs you want to see, let me know.

https://remywiki.com/CS_DDR_EXTRA_MIX
